                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3230" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0435</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8970 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">仓单变形记：青岛港仓单质押融资业务的流程改进之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The metamorphosis of Warehouse receipts: Process improvement of the warehouse pledge financing in Qingdao Port</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王崇锋，巩杰，杨箫，孟星辰，许鹏飞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛港有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">仓储部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">仓储公司；信贷风险；信息不对称；仓单质押融资业务</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Warehouse company; Credit risk; Information asymmetry; Warehouse receipts financing </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014年6月6日，青岛港国际股份有限公司在中国香港地区的联合交易所主板成功挂牌上市。然而就在上市前夕，一家在该港口存储货物的贸易公司被曝出涉及虚假贸易融资欺诈事件（以下简称“青岛港事件”）。“青岛港事件”中“德正系”涉嫌利用有色金属的仓单在多家银行重复获取融资。境内外多家银行、贸易商、担保公司也被卷入“德正系”与青岛港事件的风波之中。青岛港事件为什么会发生？曾是融资新宠的创新模式，仓单质押为何一夜之间成为众矢之的？如何防止下一个青岛港事件？本案例基于信息不对称理论，详细描述了此次事件发生的原因、影响及青岛港为规避仓单融资业务存在的风险所采取的改进措施，希望学生通过该案例的讨论学习掌握仓单质押融资业务存在的风险漏洞及相应的风险规避措施，并应用到实际工作的仓单质押融资风险管控中。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Qingdao Port International Co., Ltd. successfully listed on the Main Board of the Hong Kong Stock Exchange on June 6, 2014,. However, just before the listing, a trading company that stored goods in the port was exposed to fraudulent incidents involving false trade finance (hereinafter referred to as the “Qingdao Port incident”). In the &quot;Qingdao Port Incident,&quot; &quot;Dezhengxi&quot; was suspected of using non-ferrous metal warehouse receipts to repeatedly obtain financing at several banks. Many domestic and foreign banks, traders, and guarantee companies have been involved in the turmoil of the Qingdao port incident. Why did the Qingdao port incident occur? Why did pledge by warehouse receipts that once was the innovative mode of financing new darling become a target of public criticism overnight? How to prevent the next Qingdao port incident? This case is based on the theory of information asymmetry and describes the causes and impacts of this incident and the improvement measures adopted by Qingdao Port to avoid the risks of warehouse receipt financing business in detail. It is hoped that students will learn to grasp the warehouse receipt pledge financing and the risk loopholes in the business and corresponding risk aversion measures through the discussion of this case, which will be applied to the actual work of warehouse receipt pledge financing risk control.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《国际贸易实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">仓单质押业务</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-06</td>
                            </tr>
